                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57">cvwb</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57"> </span><span class="pt-000001491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57">Av‡Q</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(V=π{r}^{2}h=3\times {\left(\frac{4}{2}\right)}^{2}\times 10=3\times 4\times 10=120\ {m}^{3}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001491d4e98-9412-4a77-8f68-3b73febade57 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000089929c2e-0dad-4d72-b83e-f1ee99ba517b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000189929c2e-0dad-4d72-b83e-f1ee99ba517b">cvwbi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000189929c2e-0dad-4d72-b83e-f1ee99ba517b"> fi, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(m=ρv=120\times 1000\ kg=120000\ kg\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000089929c2e-0dad-4d72-b83e-f1ee99ba517b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000189929c2e-0dad-4d72-b83e-f1ee99ba517b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972"> </span><span class="pt-0000020d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972">&#255;gZv</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000020d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(p=\frac{{mgh}_{avg}\ }{t}=\frac{120000\times 10\times \frac{10}{2}}{20\times 60\times 750}\ =\frac{20}{3}=6.67≈6.87\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972"> </span><span class="pt-0000030d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972">hp</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000020d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000030d21c6c2-0057-42ef-a6bf-cfb47c71e972 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">[</span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">j&#182;Yxq</span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63"> †</span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">h‡nZz</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63"> </span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">K&#168;vjKz‡jU</span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">‡i</span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63">i</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c-cae435055d63"> </span><span class="pt-000001270b0601-4782-4481-887c