                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000715a6620-5d0c-457e-9089-3030f1b48f57" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({T}_{new}=1.5T\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001715a6620-5d0c-457e-9089-3030f1b48f57"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000715a6620-5d0c-457e-9089-3030f1b48f57 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001715a6620-5d0c-457e-9089-3030f1b48f57 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579">Avgiv</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579"> </span><span class="pt-000001f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579">Rvwb</span><span class="pt-000001f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579">,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(T=2π\sqrt{\frac{l}{g}}∴\frac{{T}_{new}}{T}=\sqrt{\frac{{l}_{new}}{l}}\ ⇒{\left(1.5\right)}^{2}\times l={l}_{new}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002f229142a-9b8e-4440-a9f9-1f3fc014a579 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000081262714-121f-4671-8528-080dc8d6e4ba" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">