                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000776aafd7-15e9-4d32-b739-d7f8f4b1439b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({E}_{k}=\frac{1}{2}\frac{{p}^{2}}{m}∴{E}_{final}=1.44\ {E}_{initial}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001776aafd7-15e9-4d32-b739-d7f8f4b1439b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000776aafd7-15e9-4d32-b739-d7f8f4b1439b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001776aafd7-15e9-4d32-b739-d7f8f4b1439b {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c15e1c7a-4faa-4bd4-8199-41b406c5afe5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴{P}_{final}=\sqrt{2m(1.44\ {E}_{initial})}=1.2\ {P}_{initial}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c15e1c7a-4faa-4bd4-8199-41b406c5afe5"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c15e1c7a-4faa-4bd4-8199-41b406c5afe5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c15e1c7a-4faa-4bd4-8199-41b406c5afe5 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001b9a03c5-eb2a-46ae-96f4-43c4128e2a1b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011b9a03c5-eb2a-46ae-96f4-43c4128e2a1b"> 1.</span><span class="pt-0000011b9a03c5-eb2a-46ae-96f4-43c4128e2a1b">2</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011b9a03c5-eb2a-46ae-96f4-43c4128e2a1b"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000021b9a03c5-eb2a-46ae-96f4-43c4128e2a1b">&#184;Y </span><span class="pt-0000021b9a03c5-eb2a-46ae-96f4-43c4128e2a1b">n‡e</span><s